fields.name: ABAR HOTEL APARTMENTS
fields.description:
You're eligible for a Genius discount at ABAR HOTEL APARTMENTS DIP-1! To save at this property, all you have to do is sign in.

ABAR HOTEL APARTMENTS DIP-1 features a sauna and spa facilities, as well as air-conditioned accommodations with free Wifi in Miami, 6.1 miles from Miami FC Stadium. There's a private entrance at the apartment for the convenience of those who stay. There's a restaurant serving American cuisine, free private parking, and an an electric vehicle charging station. The apartment provides guests with a balcony, garden views, a seating area, satellite flat-screen TV, a fully equipped kitchen with an oven and a microwave, and a private bathroom with walk-in shower and bathrobes. A toaster, a fridge, and stovetop are also available, as well as a coffee machine and a kettle. At the apartment complex, each unit includes bed linen and towels. Continental and Italian breakfast options with local specialities, fresh pastries, and pancakes are available each morning at ABAR HOTEL APARTMENTS DIP-1. There is a coffee shop, and a grocery delivery service and packed lunches are also available. For guests with children, the accommodation offers indoor and outdoor play areas. Guests can also relax in the garden, next to the rooftop pool, on the sun terrace, or in the shared lounge area. Miami FC Stadium is 6.9 miles from ABAR HOTEL APARTMENTS DIP-1, while The Skyviews Miami Ferris Wheel is 9.2 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Miami International Airport, 14 miles from the apartment, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.

 

ABAR HOTEL APARTMENTS DIP-1 has been welcoming Booking.com guests since Apr 5, 2021

fields.name: Hotel Bella Italia
fields.description: Hotel Bella Italia is a charming boutique hotel nestled in the heart of Tuscany, offering an authentic Italian experience. With elegant rooms featuring traditional decor, modern amenities, and stunning views of rolling vineyards or historic streets, the hotel provides a perfect blend of comfort and culture. Guests can enjoy fine dining at the on-site restaurant, which serves regional specialties paired with local wines. Its central location allows easy access to nearby attractions, including historic landmarks and scenic countryside. Ideal for romantic getaways or cultural escapes, Hotel Bella Italia promises a memorable stay.

fields.name: Riad Al Zahara
fields.description: Riad Al Zahara is a luxurious hotel located in the heart of Marrakech, Morocco, offering an authentic Moroccan experience. Set within a traditional riad, the hotel features intricately designed rooms with vibrant tile work, ornate wooden carvings, and plush furnishings that reflect the rich local culture. Guests can unwind in the serene courtyard with a central fountain, relax in the rooftop terrace with panoramic views of the medina, or enjoy authentic Moroccan cuisine at the on-site restaurant. Conveniently located near famous souks and historic landmarks like the Koutoubia Mosque, Riad Al Zahara is a tranquil retreat ideal for cultural explorers and those seeking a romantic escape.

fields.name: Hotel Sol y Mar
fields.description:
Hotel Sol y Mar is a luxurious beachfront hotel located on Spain's stunning Costa del Sol. Featuring modern, spacious rooms with private balconies overlooking the Mediterranean Sea, it offers a perfect blend of relaxation and elegance. The hotel boasts a rooftop pool, a full-service spa, and several fine dining options serving both local Spanish cuisine and international dishes. Its prime location allows guests to easily explore nearby attractions, including vibrant seaside towns, cultural landmarks, and golf courses. Whether you're seeking a sun-soaked getaway or a cultural escape, Hotel Sol y Mar delivers an unforgettable experience.

fields.name: Hotel Adriatica
fields.description: Hotel Adriatica is a stunning seaside hotel located along the picturesque Dalmatian Coast in Croatia. Offering modern, elegant rooms with floor-to-ceiling windows and private balconies, guests enjoy breathtaking views of the Adriatic Sea. The hotel features an infinity pool, a rooftop bar, and a restaurant serving fresh Mediterranean cuisine with local Croatian flavors. Located near charming coastal towns and historic sites like Diocletian's Palace, Hotel Adriatica is the perfect base for exploring Croatia�s islands, beaches, and cultural landmarks. Ideal for both relaxation and adventure, it promises a memorable Croatian getaway.
